## Guardrails

- Function ≤ **{{.Guardrails.MaxFunctionLines}}** lines. Split with helpers when you cross.
- File ≤ **{{.Guardrails.MaxFileLines}}** lines.
{{- if .Guardrails.RequireTests}}
- New code carries tests. Bug fixes carry regression tests.
{{- end}}
- Validate inputs at every boundary. Parameterise queries. No magic numbers, no commented-out code, no TODOs without a tracker.
- Conventional commits: `type(scope): description`. One logical change per commit.
